{"word":"H6937 - קָדַר - qâdar - kaw-dar' - Be black - கருப்பாயிரு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>קָדַר"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>qâdar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kaw-dar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be black / கருப்பாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கறுத்துப்போதல், கறுத்திரு, இருண்டுபோ, காரிருளாய்ப் போ, துக்கித்திரு, கலங்கலாகு, இருளடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to mourn, to be dark"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to be dark"},{"paragraph":"b) (Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"1) to darken"},{"paragraph":"2) to cause to mourn"},{"paragraph":"c) (Hithpael) to grow dark"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>be ashy</i>, that is, <i>dark</i> colored; by implication to <i>mourn</i> (in sackcloth or sordid garments): - be black (-ish), be (make) dark (-en), X heavily, (cause to) mourn."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6937 - קָדַר - qâdar - kaw-dar'/6937\">H6937</a>, <a href=\"#/H6938 - קֵדָר - Qêdâr - kay-dawr'/6938\">H6938</a>, <a href=\"#/H6939 - קִדְרֹון - Qidrôwn - kid-rone'/6939\">H6939</a>, <a href=\"#/H6940 - קַדְרוּת - qadrûwth - kad-rooth'/6940\">H6940</a>, <a href=\"#/H6941 - קְדֹרַנִּית - qᵉdôrannîyth - ked-o-ran-neeth'/6941\">H6941</a>"}]}